flowRoot.flowPara: The next step is to submit the changes to the team project. In your web browser, open the master project on github and click the "Compare & Pull Request" button.
As the team project advances, you'll need to update origin and master. We'll do this by updating master first.
As a good rule of thumb, you should always update origin by pushing from master.
We'll call it patch. The following command creates the branch and switches you to it.
